race.comment: Open race to close out the card. KETTLEBELL (13) has placed over this track and trip and will strip fitter third-up from the break. Can improve enough to take this out. The well-related PEE BEE NOIR (11) (half to G1 winner Atlante) boasts a win around this circuit and will find this easier than the recent effort in town. Top-three commodity on best figures. BOLD AS BRASS (1) saves his best form for this six-furlong journey and can feature with any luck in running. THIEM (7) has kicked off his campaign with consecutive placings across the border. Warrants consideration third run from a spell at an each way quote.
